            <title>ASUS 推出金色版 RTX 5090，奢华设计瞄准中东市场</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/06/asus-rog-astral-rtx5090-gold/wireless-home/desktop-pc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=asus-rog-astral-rtx5090-gold</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/06/asus-rog-astral-rtx5090-gold/wireless-home/desktop-pc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 13:30:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌上电脑]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290274</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>华硕（ASUS）近日发布 ROG Astral GeForce RTX 5090 Dhahab Gold Edition，这款显示卡采用金色外观与中东风格设计，展现该地区的繁荣与奢华。整体造型金碧辉煌，辅以祖母绿点缀细节，风扇轴心镶嵌金色 ROG 标志，背面更融入摩天大楼天际线，象征中东城市从沙漠崛起，迈向现代化发展的历程。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/psu-629x580.jpg" alt="" width="629" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/psu-629x580.jpg 629w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/psu.jpg 900w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 629px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290278" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdback-694x397.png" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdback-694x397.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdback.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲背面刻有摩天大楼天际线，图片来源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a></p><p>「Dhahab」在阿拉伯语中意为黄金，这款显示卡外观耀眼，细节亦精雕细琢。正面镶刻阿拉伯书法，融入「力量、勇气、团结」等字样，展现当地文化底蕴。框架采用全金属压铸工艺，并搭载镀金 GPU 支架，提升结构稳固度，亦增添尊贵感与耐用性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura-694x568.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="568" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura-694x568.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura.jpg 912w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a></p><p>技术规格方面，Dhahab Gold Edition 与标准版 ROG Astral RTX 5090 规格一致，采用四风扇散热系统、均热板导热技术、高密度散热鳍片，以及强化供电设计，确保运行效能稳定，发挥极致表现。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura-694x568.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="568" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura-694x568.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura.jpg 912w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a></p><p>华硕目前尚未公布此特别版售价。标准版 RTX 5090 Astral 官方定价 3,079 美元（约港币 23,978 元），市场普遍存在溢价，预计这款限量版 Dhahab Gold Edition 价格将再创新高。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290277" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pd-694x397.png" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pd-694x397.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pd.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a>、<a href="https://videocardz.com/newz/asus-unveils-rog-astral-geforce-rtx-5090-dhahab-gold-edition">Video Cardz</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/06/asus-rog-astral-rtx5090-gold/wireless-home/desktop-pc/">ASUS 推出金色版 RTX 5090，奢华设计瞄准中东市场</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
